#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.145"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.145:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.145:0.2"
msgid "15. Tikaṇḍakīvagga "
msgstr "15. At Tikaṇḍakī "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.145:0.3"
msgid "145. Nirayasutta "
msgstr "145. Hell "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.145:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with five qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an5.145:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.145:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī hoti, musāvādī hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī hoti. "
msgstr "They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.145:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.171, sc2
msgctxt "an5.145:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "Someone with five qualities is raised up to heaven "

msgctxt "an5.145:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.145:2.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti. "
msgstr "They don’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.145:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is raised up to heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.145:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

